title: What happened with Androgenic? Unexpected on-camera moment goes viral within hours
summary_full: A viral video showing Androgenic’s hat being pulled off sparked major debate online. Viewers questioned his image after seeing what appeared to be a receding hairline. The term “fraudmaxxer” trended on X, and some online rankings reportedly dropped him. While the video’s authenticity remains unverified, the incident has fueled discussion about honesty in the self-improvement world.
